---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Patch v0.103.2">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>v0.103.2 Balance Patch</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Changes from v0.101.0 &rarr; v0.103.2 &mdash; derived from decompiled game data</p>
  </div>

  <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">

    <p class="desc-text">
      v0.103.2 is a content and balance patch. Three new relics (Neow's Bones, Phial Holster, Winged Boots)
      join the pool, a new <a href={`${base}enchantments/inky/`}>Inky</a> enchantment drives a
      <a href={`${base}cards/blade-of-ink/`}>Blade of Ink</a> rework, Borrowed Time becomes a Colorless
      energy-burst card with its own stacking power, and Grasp is redesigned to drain Energy per card
      played. Several cards move between characters, Living Fog's Bloat is brought down to one minion,
      and the <code>IsAllowed(IRunState)</code> API refactor touches every event class but affects no
      gameplay.
    </p>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- CARDS                           -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="cards" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Card Changes</h2>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--green);">New Card</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Card</th><th>Character</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}cards/not-yet/`}>Not Yet</a></td>
          <td class="char-ironclad">Ironclad</td>
          <td>2-cost Rare Skill. <strong>Exhaust</strong>. "Heal 10 HP." Upgrade: heal 13 HP.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--red-bright);">Removed Card</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Card</th><th>Character</th><th>Was</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Grapple</td>
          <td class="char-ironclad">Ironclad</td>
          <td>1-cost Uncommon Attack. 7/9 damage plus Grasp.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent);">Major Reworks</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Card</th><th>Character</th><th>Before</th><th>After</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}cards/blade-of-ink/`}>Blade of Ink</a></td>
          <td class="char-regent">Regent</td>
          <td>"This turn, whenever you play an Attack, gain 2 Strength this turn."</td>
          <td>"Add 2 <a href={`${base}enchantments/inky/`}>Inky</a> Shivs into your Hand." Upgrade: 3 Shivs.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}cards/borrowed-time/`}>Borrowed Time</a></td>
          <td>Necrobinder &rarr; <strong>Colorless</strong></td>
          <td>0-cost Skill. Apply 3 Doom. Gain 1 Energy. <em>(Upgrade: Gain 2 Energy)</em></td>
          <td>1-cost Skill. "Gain 4 Energy. Cards cost an additional 1 Energy this turn." Applies stacking <a href={`${base}powers/borrowed-time/`}>Borrowed Time</a>.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}cards/follow-through/`}>Follow Through</a></td>
          <td>Silent &rarr; <strong>Ironclad</strong></td>
          <td>Uncommon. 6/8 AoE damage; if last card was a Skill, apply 1/2 Weak to all enemies.</td>
          <td><strong>Common</strong>. 7/9 single-target damage; hits an additional time if you have 5+ other cards in hand.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent);">Character Transfers</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Card</th><th>Before</th><th>After</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/flak-cannon/`}>Flak Cannon</a></td><td>Ironclad</td><td>Colorless (now targets a random enemy instead of all)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/flanking/`}>Flanking</a></td><td>Token</td><td>Colorless</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/guards/`}>Guards</a></td><td>Colorless</td><td>Necrobinder</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/memento-mori/`}>Memento Mori</a></td><td>Necrobinder</td><td>Colorless</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/rocket-punch/`}>Rocket Punch</a></td><td>Defect</td><td>Ironclad</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/seeking-edge/`}>Seeking Edge</a></td><td>Ironclad</td><td>Regent</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent);">Stat &amp; Rarity Changes</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Card</th><th>Character</th><th>Change</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/acrobatics/`}>Acrobatics</a></td><td class="char-silent">Silent</td><td>Rarity: Common &rarr; <strong>Uncommon</strong>.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/colossus/`}>Colossus</a></td><td class="char-ironclad">Ironclad</td><td>Rarity: Rare &rarr; <strong>Uncommon</strong>.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/leading-strike/`}>Leading Strike</a></td><td class="char-silent">Silent</td><td>Damage 7/10 &rarr; <strong>3/6</strong>; Shivs generated 1 &rarr; <strong>2</strong>.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/memento-mori/`}>Memento Mori</a></td><td>Colorless</td><td>Base damage 8/10 &rarr; <strong>9/11</strong>.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/speedster/`}>Speedster</a></td><td class="char-ironclad">Ironclad</td><td>Upgrade now grants <strong>Innate</strong> instead of +1 damage.</td></tr>
        <tr><td><a href={`${base}cards/untouchable/`}>Untouchable</a></td><td class="char-silent">Silent</td><td>Block 7/9 &rarr; <strong>6/8</strong>.</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- POWERS                          -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="powers" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Power Changes</h2>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--green);">New Power</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Power</th><th>Effect</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}powers/borrowed-time/`}>Borrowed Time</a></td>
          <td>Cards cost an additional Energy this turn. Stacks.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--red-bright);">Removed Powers</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Power</th><th>Reason</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Blade of Ink</td><td>Replaced by the new Inky enchantment that Blade of Ink now produces.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Grapple</td><td>Removed alongside the Grapple card.</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent);">Reworks</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Power</th><th>Before</th><th>After</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}powers/grasp/`}>Grasp</a></td>
          <td>The first card you play each turn costs 1 additional Energy.</td>
          <td><strong>Whenever you play a card, lose 1 Energy.</strong> Now applies Weighted afflictions to cards in hand.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}powers/flanking/`}>Flanking</a></td>
          <td>Other allies deal 2x more damage to this enemy this turn.</td>
          <td>Other allies deal 2x more <strong>attack</strong> damage to this enemy this turn.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- ENCHANTMENTS                    -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="enchantments" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Enchantments</h2>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--green);">New Enchantment</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Enchantment</th><th>Effect</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}enchantments/inky/`}>Inky</a></td>
          <td>The enchanted card deals 2 additional damage and applies 1 Weak. Produced by the reworked Blade of Ink.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- RELICS                          -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="relics" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Relic Changes</h2>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--green);">New Relics</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Relic</th><th>Rarity</th><th>Effect</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}relics/neow-s-bones/`}>Neow's Bones</a></td>
          <td>Event</td>
          <td>Upon pickup, gain 2 random Neow Relics. Add 1 random Curse to your Deck.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}relics/phial-holster/`}>Phial Holster</a></td>
          <td>Event</td>
          <td>Upon pickup, gain 1 potion slot and procure 2 random potions.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}relics/winged-boots/`}>Winged Boots</a></td>
          <td>Uncommon</td>
          <td>You may ignore paths when choosing the next rooms to travel to, up to 3 times.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent);">Relic Tweaks</h3>
    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Relic</th><th>Change</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}relics/fragrant-mushroom/`}>Fragrant Mushroom</a></td>
          <td>Upgrades: 3 cards &rarr; <strong>2 cards</strong>. HP cost unchanged at 15.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}relics/regalite/`}>Regalite</a></td>
          <td>"Whenever you create a <strong>Colorless</strong> card" &rarr; "Whenever you create <strong>a</strong> card" (now triggers on any created card).</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="desc-text" style="font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      Additional text/flavor polish: Archaic Tooth, Beautiful Bracelet, Belt Buckle, Fur Coat, History Course,
      Large Capsule, Lord's Parasol, Massive Scroll, Pael's Tooth, Scroll Boxes, Silver Crucible, Unsettling Lamp,
      Whispering Earring, Wing Charm.
    </p>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- MONSTERS                        -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="monsters" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Monster Changes</h2>

    <table class="stat-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Monster</th><th>Change</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}monsters/living-fog/`}>Living Fog</a></td>
          <td>Bloat no longer escalates: now spawns exactly 1 Gas Bomb per use instead of 1-5.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}monsters/doormaker/`}>Doormaker</a></td>
          <td>Hunger damage rebalanced (ascension value notably higher, base lower). Scrutiny damage lowered.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><a href={`${base}monsters/thieving-hopper/`}>Thieving Hopper</a></td>
          <td>Card-stealing now skips dead targets instead of potentially stalling.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="desc-text" style="font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      Other monsters with data-level tweaks: Bygone Effigy, Byrdonis, Calcified Cultist, Chomper,
      Crossbow Ruby Raider, Damp Cultist, Devoted Sculptor, Fake Merchant Monster, Fat Gremlin,
      Gremlin Merc, Kin Follower, Kin Priest, Knowledge Demon, Lagavulin Matriarch, Magi Knight, Queen,
      Skulking Colony, Test Subject, The Insatiable, Two-Tailed Rat, Vantom, Waterfall Giant.
      Most are small cleanups or VFX polish.
    </p>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- POTIONS                         -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="potions" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Potion Changes</h2>
    <p class="desc-text">
      <a href={`${base}potions/foul-potion/`}>Foul Potion</a> had its internal description text updated
      (mechanics unchanged).
    </p>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- EVENTS                          -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ -->
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="events" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Events</h2>
    <p class="desc-text">
      Nine events received content/balance tweaks, most subtle:
      Battleworn Dummy, Colorful Philosophers, Self-Help Book, Spiraling Whirlpool, Tablet of Truth,
      The Architect, Trial, Waterlogged Scriptorium, Whispering Hollow.
    </p>
    <p class="desc-text" style="font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      Note: every event class also received the <code>IsAllowed(RunState)</code> &rarr;
      <code>IsAllowed(IRunState)</code> signature refactor. This is an internal API change only; no
      behavior is affected.
    </p>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
